<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>管理后台 · 灵山胜境</title>
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{font-family:"Microsoft YaHei",sans-serif;background:#0a0e17;color:#c0c8d8;min-height:100vh;display:flex}
.sidebar{width:220px;background:#111827;border-right:1px solid #1f2937;padding:20px 0;min-height:100vh}
.sidebar .logo{text-align:center;padding:20px;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f5af19,#f12711);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent}
.nav-item{padding:14px 24px;cursor:pointer;color:#9ca3af;border-left:3px solid transparent;transition:.3s;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.nav-item:hover,.nav-item.active{background:rgba(255,215,0,.05);color:#FFD700;border-left-color:#FFD700}
.main{flex:1;padding:30px}
.page-title{font-size:24px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:24px;color:#fff}
.stats-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:20px;margin-bottom:30px}
.stat-card{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1f2e,#1f2937);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;border:1px solid #2a3347}
.stat-card .label{font-size:13px;color:#9ca3af;margin-bottom:8px}
.stat-card .value{font-size:36px;font-weight:bold;color:#FFD700}
.stat-card .sub{font-size:12px;color:#6b7280;margin-top:4px}
.chart-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px}
.chart-card{background:#111827;border-radius:16px;padding:24px;border:1px solid #1f2937}
.chart-card h3{font-size:16px;color:#e5e7eb;margin-bottom:16px}
.hot-item{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1f2937}
.hot-item .rank{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;background:#1f2937;color:#9ca3af}
.hot-item .rank.top1{background:#FFD700;color:#1a1a2e}.hot-item .rank.top2{background:#c0c0c0;color:#1a1a2e}.hot-item .rank.top3{background:#cd7f32;color:#1a1a2e}
.hot-item .q-text{flex:1;margin-left:12px;font-size:14px}
.hot-item .q-count{color:#FFD700;font-weight:bold}
.sentiment-bar{height:8px;border-radius:4px;background:#1f2937;margin-top:8px;overflow:hidden}
.sentiment-bar .fill{height:100%;border-radius:4px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#f12711,#f5af19,#00ff88)}
.page{display:none}.page.active{display:block}
.file-list{background:#111827;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #1f2937}
.file-item{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:14px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid #1f2937}
.file-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.tag{padding:4px 10px;border-radius:12px;font-size:11px;background:rgba(0,255,136,.1);color:#00ff88}
</style></head>
<body>
<div class="sidebar">
<div class="logo">🏯 灵山管理台</div>
<div class="nav-item active" onclick="showPage('dashboard')">📊 数据大屏</div>
<div class="nav-item" onclick="showPage('knowledge')">📚 知识库管理</div>
<div class="nav-item" onclick="showPage('report')">📈 游客报告</div>
<div class="nav-item" onclick="window.open('/')">💬 游客端</div>
</div>
<div class="main">
<div class="page active" id="page-dashboard">
<div class="page-title">📊 运营数据大屏</div>
<div class="stats-grid">
<div class="stat-card"><div class="label">👥 今日服务人次</div><div class="value">1,280</div><div class="sub">较昨日 ↑12%</div></div>
<div class="stat-card"><div class="label">💬 本周累计问答</div><div class="value">8,920</div><div class="sub">日均 1,274 次</div></div>
<div class="stat-card"><div class="label">😊 游客满意度</div><div class="value">95.2<span style="font-size:18px">%</span></div><div class="sub">基于 3,280 条反馈</div></div>
<div class="stat-card"><div class="label">⚡ 平均响应</div><div class="value">2.8<span style="font-size:18px">s</span></div><div class="sub">P95: 4.2s</div></div>
</div>
<div class="chart-row">
<div class="chart-card"><h3>🔥 热门问题 Top 5</h3>
<div class="hot-item"><span class="rank top1">1</span><span class="q-text">灵山大佛有多高</span><span class="q-count">245次</span></div>
<div class="hot-item"><span class="rank top2">2</span><span class="q-text">门票多少钱</span><span class="q-count">189次</span></div>
<div class="hot-item"><span class="rank top3">3</span><span class="q-text">游览路线推荐</span><span class="q-count">156次</span></div>
<div class="hot-item"><span class="rank">4</span><span class="q-text">灵山胜境在哪</span><span class="q-count">134次</span></div>
<div class="hot-item"><span class="rank">5</span><span class="q-text">九龙灌浴表演时间</span><span class="q-count">98次</span></div>
</div>
<div class="chart-card"><h3>📈 一周问答趋势</h3>
<div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:12px;height:180px;padding-top:20px">
<div style="flex:1;text-align:center"><div style="background:linear-gradient(180deg,#FFD700,#B8860B);height:100px;border-radius:8px"></div><span style="font-size:11px;color:#9ca3af">周一</span></div>
<div style="flex:1;text-align:center"><div style="background:linear-gradient(180deg,#FFD700,#B8860B);height:130px;border-radius:8px"></div><span style="font-size:11px;color:#9ca3af">周二</span></div>
<div style="flex:1;text-align:center"><div style="background:linear-gradient(180deg,#FFD700,#B8860B);height:90px;border-radius:8px"></div><span style="font-size:11px;color:#9ca3af">周三</span></div>
<div style="flex:1;text-align:center"><div style="background:linear-gradient(180deg,#FFD700,#B8860B);height:150px;border-radius:8px"></div><span style="font-size:11px;color:#9ca3af">周四</span></div>
<div style="flex:1;text-align:center"><div style="background:linear-gradient(180deg,#FFD700,#B8860B);height:140px;border-radius:8px"></div><span style="font-size:11px;color:#9ca3af">周五</span></div>
<div style="flex:1;text-align:center"><div style="background:linear-gradient(180deg,#FFD700,#B8860B);height:170px;border-radius:8px"></div><span style="font-size:11px;color:#9ca3af">周六</span></div>
<div style="flex:1;text-align:center"><div style="background:linear-gradient(180deg,#FFD700,#B8860B);height:80px;border-radius:8px"></div><span style="font-size:11px;color:#9ca3af">周日</span></div>
</div></div></div></div>
<div class="page" id="page-knowledge">
<div class="page-title">📚 知识库文档管理</div>
<div style="border:2px dashed #2a3347;border-radius:16px;padding:40px;text-align:center;margin-bottom:20px"><div style="font-size:48px;margin-bottom:8px">📁</div><p style="color:#9ca3af">点击上传文档（支持 PDF/Word/TXT）</p></div>
<div class="file-list">
<div class="file-item"><div>📄 灵山胜境景点结构化数据集.txt</div><span class="tag">已索引</span></div>
<div class="file-item"><div>📄 灵山胜境游览指南.txt</div><span class="tag">已索引</span></div>
<div class="file-item"><div>📊 旅游数据行为分析.xlsx</div><span class="tag" style="background:rgba(255,215,0,.1);color:#FFD700">待处理</span></div>
</div></div>
<div class="page" id="page-report">
<div class="page-title">📈 游客感受度报告</div>
<div class="chart-row">
<div class="chart-card"><h3>😊 情感分析</h3><div style="font-size:48px;text-align:center;color:#00ff88;padding:20px">92.5%</div><div style="text-align:center;color:#9ca3af">正面反馈占比</div><div class="sentiment-bar" style="margin-top:16px"><div class="fill" style="width:92.5%"></div></div></div>
<div class="chart-card"><h3>💡 服务优化建议</h3><div style="padding:12px;color:#c0c8d8;line-height:2">💬 增加夜间游览项目<br>🌍 多语言讲解需求上升<br>📱 小程序预约功能优化<br>🚌 观光车班次加密建议</div></div>
</div></div>
</div>
<script>function showPage(name){document.querySelectorAll('.page').forEach(p=>p.classList.remove('active'));document.getElementById('page-'+name).classList.add('active');document.querySelectorAll('.nav-item').forEach(n=>n.classList.remove('active'));event.target.closest('.nav-item').classList.add('active')}</script>
</body></html>